### STEP 2: Custom Object Creation

#### 2.1 Property Object

**Navigation:** Setup → Object Manager → Create → Custom Object

**Configuration:**

| Setting | Value |
|---------|-------|
| Label | Property |
| Plural Label | Properties |
| Record Name | Property Name |
| Data Type | Text |

**Property Fields:**

| Field Name | Type | Description |
|------------|------|-------------|
| Property_Name | Text(80) | Property identifier |
| Property_Type | Picklist | Residential/Commercial/Industrial |
| Location | Text Area | Full address |
| Area_Sq_Ft | Number(10,2) | Property size |
| Monthly_Rent | Currency | Rent amount |
| Property_Status | Picklist | Available/Occupied/Maintenance |
| Number_of_Rooms | Number | Room count |

#### 2.2 Tenant Object

**Tenant Fields:**

| Field Name | Type | Description |
|------------|------|-------------|
| Tenant_Name | Text(80) | Full name |
| Email | Email | Contact email |
| Phone_Number | Phone | Mobile number |
| ID_Proof_Type | Picklist | Aadhar/PAN/Passport |
| ID_Proof_Number | Text(50) | Document number |
| Property | Lookup(Property) | Associated property |
| Emergency_Contact | Phone | Emergency number |

#### 2.3 Lease Object

**Lease Fields:**

| Field Name | Type | Description |
|------------|------|-------------|
| Lease_Number | Auto Number | Format: LS-{0000} |
| Property | Lookup(Property) | Leased property |
| Tenant | Lookup(Tenant) | Tenant details |
| Lease_Start_Date | Date | Start date |
| Lease_End_Date | Date | End date |
| Monthly_Rent | Currency | Rent amount |
| Security_Deposit | Currency | Deposit amount |
| Lease_Status | Picklist | Pending/Active/Expired |
| Payment_Frequency | Picklist | Monthly/Quarterly |

#### 2.4 Payment Object

**Payment Fields:**

| Field Name | Type | Description |
|------------|------|-------------|
| Payment_Number | Auto Number | Format: PAY-{0000} |
