| Tenant | Lookup(Tenant) | Paying tenant |
| Payment_Date | Date | Transaction date |
| Due_Date | Date | Payment due date |
| Amount_Paid | Currency | Payment amount |
| Payment_Method | Picklist | Cash/Online/UPI |
| Payment_Status | Picklist | Pending/Paid/Overdue |
| Transaction_ID | Text(100) | Reference number |

