### STEP 5: Validation Rules

**Purpose:** Ensure data quality and prevent errors

**Validation Rules Table:**

| Object | Rule Name | Condition | Error Message |
|--------|-----------|-----------|---------------|
| Lease | End_Date_After_Start | Lease_End_Date__c <= Lease_Start_Date__c | "End date must be after start date" |
| Payment | Positive_Amount | Amount_Paid__c <= 0 | "Amount must be greater than zero" |
| Property | Valid_Rent | Monthly_Rent__c < 0 | "Rent cannot be negative" |
| Payment | No_Future_Payment | Payment_Date__c > TODAY() | "Payment date cannot be future" |

