## 5. AUTOMATION FEATURES

### STEP 6: Email Templates

**Navigation:** Setup → Classic Email Templates → New Template

#### Email Templates Summary

| Template Name | Trigger | Recipient |
|---------------|---------|-----------|
| Tenant_Leaving_Notification | Vacancy request | Admin |
| Lease_Approved | Lease approved | Tenant |
| Lease_Rejection | Lease rejected | Tenant |
| Monthly_Payment_Reminder | 3 days before due | Tenant |
| Payment_Confirmation | Payment completed | Tenant |

#### Template 1: Lease Approved

```
Subject: Lease Application Approved

Dear {!Lease__c.Tenant__r.Tenant_Name__c},

Your lease application has been approved!

Lease Details:
- Property: {!Lease__c.Property__r.Property_Name__c}
- Start Date: {!Lease__c.Lease_Start_Date__c}
- End Date: {!Lease__c.Lease_End_Date__c}
- Monthly Rent: ₹{!Lease__c.Monthly_Rent__c}
- Security Deposit: ₹{!Lease__c.Security_Deposit__c}

Welcome!
Property Management Team
```

#### Template 2: Payment Reminder

```
Subject: Rent Payment Reminder

Dear {!Payment__c.Tenant__r.Tenant_Name__c},

Your rent payment is due soon.

Amount Due: ₹{!Payment__c.Amount_Paid__c}
Due Date: {!Payment__c.Due_Date__c}

Please pay on time to avoid late fees.

Thank you,
Finance Team
```

